  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育平台设计一个状态流转图，核心是课堂服务的状态变化。起点是Education_ClassroomService，它初始状态应该是静止的Still状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以ClassroomService启动后进入Still状态。那Still状态之后有哪些去向？是只能单向流转还是可以循环？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Still有两个去向：一是同步成绩到Education_GradeSync，这是业务上的数据上报；二是进入Moving状态，代表课堂开始活跃、有实时互动发生。这两个是并行的，不是二选一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Still同时连到GradeSync和Moving。那Moving状态呢？课堂活跃之后怎么流转？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Moving可以回到Still，比如课堂互动结束恢复平静；也可能发生异常进入Crash状态。Crash是个终止性状态，但需要把错误日志和资源快照推送到Education_ContentCDN做持久化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画一下：Moving双向连回Still，同时单向指向Crash，Crash再连到ContentCDN。这样Crash没有出边，符合终止态的设计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Moving到Still的箭头方向我刚才没说清楚——应该是双向的，但含义不同：Moving可以主动回到Still，Still也可以在特定条件下重新激活为Moving。不过你画的单向回退也可以，我确认一下：双向还是两个单向箭头？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Mermaid里画两个单向箭头更明确，表示两个独立的状态转换。我改成Moving -- Still 和 Still -- Moving 分开画，这样可读性更好。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但Still到Moving的触发条件比较少见，先保留结构。整体检查一遍：ClassroomService启动进Still，Still分叉到GradeSync和Moving，Moving可回Still或进Crash，Crash最终落地到ContentCDN。完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Still",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认最终结构，所有节点和流转关系已落实。标题用\"Simple sample\"，状态图版本用v2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "Simple sample"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
